ĹIn loving memory of HILDA MARGARET DAVIDSON (n√©e Lawday)
15th January 1951 - 29th November 2010
Beloved wife of Martin, mother of Brian & Roger and grandma to Emily & Sophie
Forever in our memories and in our hearts
God saw you getting tired and a cure was not to be,
So he put his arms around you and whispered, "Come to Me"
With tearful eyes we watched yow and saw you pass away
and, although we love you dearly, we could not make you stav.
A Golden heart stopped beating, hard working hands at rest.
God broke our hearts to prove to us, He only takes the best."„
